snippet.title: MiSTer FPGA: Atari 2600  Wolfenstein VCS (Hack of Venture)
snippet.description:
Atari 2600 Hackabrew: Wolfenstein VCS (AKA Wolfenstein 2600)
MiSTer FPGA running Atari 2600 core

Game Description:
Escape from Castle Wolfenstein again! But this time do it on your VCS! It's all there, nazis, dogs, guns, knives, chalices, med-packs, you'll never believe this was once Venture, a dungeon crawler about snakes and pots of gold!

Venture hacked by AtariAge's neotokeo2001 & Robert M 
Year: 2004

Download the ROM from AtariAge:
http://www.atariage.com/hack_page.html?SoftwareHackID=271

Buy the game from AtariAge's store:
https://atariage.com/store/index.php?l=product_detail&p=824

Mister FPGA Wiki Project:
https://github.com/MiSTer-devel/Main_MiSTer/wiki

Mister Forum discussion:
http://www.atari-forum.com/viewforum.php?f=117

Sorgelig's MiSTer Cores:
https://github.com/MiSTer-devel

MiSTer Facebook Group:
https://www.facebook.com/groups/1870135613286506/

The video clip was captured and uploaded by AVerMedia Game Capture HD II.
